#加载ggplot2绘图包和RColorBrewer画板颜色包

library(ggplot2)
## Warning: 程辑包'ggplot2'是用R版本4.2.3 来建造的
library(RColorBrewer)

#读取示例数据并查看

enrich <- read.table("Dotplot-sc_Demo3.xls", head=TRUE,sep="\t")

#绘制初始Dotplot图

p=ggplot(enrich)+
  geom_point(aes(Enrichment_score,id,fill=-log10(pval),size=ListHits))
p

#将数据按照横坐标Enrichment_score排序

enrich=enrich[order(enrich$Enrichment_score),]
enrich$id=factor(enrich$id,levels = as.character(enrich$id))
p=ggplot(enrich)+
  geom_point(aes(Enrichment_score,id,fill=-log10(pval),size=ListHits))
p

#修改点的类型为空心圆，添加新的主题图层

enrich=enrich[order(enrich$Enrichment_score),]
enrich$id=factor(enrich$id,levels = as.character(enrich$id))
p=ggplot(enrich)+
  geom_point(aes(Enrichment_score,id,fill=-log10(pval),size=ListHits), shape = 21)+
  theme_classic()
p

#选择RColorBrewer包中提供的主题颜色映射

enrich=enrich[order(enrich$Enrichment_score),]
enrich$id=factor(enrich$id,levels = as.character(enrich$id))
p=ggplot(enrich)+
  geom_point(aes(Enrichment_score,id,fill=-log10(pval),size=ListHits), shape = 21)+
  theme_classic()+
  scale_fill_distiller(palette = "Spectral")
p

#调整x轴、y轴以及图例名称

enrich=enrich[order(enrich$Enrichment_score),]
enrich$id=factor(enrich$id,levels = as.character(enrich$id))
p=ggplot(enrich)+
  geom_point(aes(Enrichment_score,id,fill=-log10(pval),size=ListHits), shape = 21)+
  theme_classic()+
  scale_fill_distiller(palette = "Spectral")+
  labs(x="Enrichment score",y="GO id",size="Number",fill= '-Log10(pval)')
p

#添加文字标注并根据Enrichment_score值区分放置位置和颜色

enrich=enrich[order(enrich$Enrichment_score),]
enrich$id=factor(enrich$id,levels = as.character(enrich$id))
enrich$position= ifelse(enrich$Enrichment_score < 0, "right", "left")
p=ggplot(enrich)+
  geom_point(aes(Enrichment_score,id,fill=-log10(pval),size=ListHits), shape = 21)+
  theme_classic()+
  scale_fill_distiller(palette = "Spectral")+
  labs(x="Enrichment score",y="GO id",size="Number",fill= '-Log10(pval)')+
  geom_text(aes(label = term,x=Enrichment_score,y=id),color =ifelse(enrich$position == "left", "Dodgerblue", "Tomato"),
hjust = ifelse(enrich$position == "left", 1.2, -0.2),nudge_x = ifelse(enrich$position == "left", -0.2, 0.2),nudge_y = 0)
p

#保存绘图结果到本地文件Dotplot-sc_Demo3.png、Dotplot-sc_Demo3.pdf中,并设置高与宽

enrich=enrich[order(enrich$Enrichment_score),]
enrich$id=factor(enrich$id,levels = as.character(enrich$id))
enrich$position= ifelse(enrich$Enrichment_score < 0, "right", "left")
p=ggplot(enrich)+
  geom_point(aes(Enrichment_score,id,fill=-log10(pval),size=ListHits), shape = 21)+
  theme_classic()+
  scale_fill_distiller(palette = "Spectral")+
  labs(x="Enrichment score",y="GO id",size="Number",fill= '-Log10(pval)')+
  geom_text(aes(label = term,x=Enrichment_score,y=id),color =ifelse(enrich$position == "left", "Dodgerblue", "Tomato"),
hjust = ifelse(enrich$position == "left", 1.2, -0.2),nudge_x = ifelse(enrich$position == "left", -0.2, 0.2),nudge_y = 0)
p

ggsave(p,file="Dotplot-sc_Demo3.png",height=7,width=8)   
ggsave(p,file="Dotplot-sc_Demo3.pdf",height=7,width=8)
